once apon a time,in a frorest there lived a monkey who resited on a berry tree,which was on the banks of a river.
In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife 
one day, the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree.
the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits.
the next day the crocodile came back for more fruits as he loved them.  